  "lease_text": "...
Section 12 – Subletting and Assignment
The Tenant may not assign this Lease, nor sublet the Premises, or any part thereof, without the prior written consent of the Landlord, which shall not be unreasonably withheld. Any unauthorized subletting shall be considered a breach of this Lease. The Tenant must submit a written request at least 30 days before the intended sublet date, providing the proposed sub‑tenant's name, contact information, and lease terms. The Landlord may require a reasonable security deposit from the sub‑tenant.
..."
